In a multi-user concurrent system.

How are we going to maintain integrity of data.

The data can be in any data-source. It is not mandate it is in database.

How are we going to allow multiple users to work on same object's with out leading them to
collusion in data.

How are we going to do this in an optimistic way. Not making our system un-popular.

Solution 1: Optimistic Offline Lock

Thing's to take in consideration : System Transaction and Business Transaction.

Reference for code and implementation:
To get a real time feel of this go through
https://docs.jboss.org/hibernate/orm/3.3/reference/en/html/transactions.html

